page.title: 04BEAULIEU VILLAGE
page.content: Beaulieu is a small village in the {New Forest.}In Beaulieu there is a school that has about 100 children in it.There is only one bank in Beaulieu and that is a {LLoyds Bank. On the main road there is a bridge going over a tidal river.The river leads to a {lake.}The lake isn't tidal. On the main road there is a chocolate shop that is {World Famous. Along the same side there are lots of private buildings. Along the other side there is an art shop that sells lots of paintings. I think the biggest attraction is the motor museum. In it there are lots of vehicles and other attractions.
